<div>
  <div class="relative text-center w-full min-h-[200px] md:min-h-[300px] text-neutral-content p-10 lg:p-30" >
    <%= image_tag "background/Nouveauprojet.png",
      class: "absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover bg-contain bg-center bg-no-repeat",
      fetchpriority: "high",
      alt: "Background image with people working together",
      loading: "eager" %>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/70"></div>
    <div class="relative z-10 reveal delay-1">
      <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-6xl ">
        <%= title "Who are <span class='text-gradient'>we?</span>".html_safe %>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl p-8 md:text-center lg:text-2xl text-primary-content ">
        <%= description "Aïkku supports digital transformation and develops scalable platforms" %>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <section class="py-16 px-8 md:p-20 reveal delay-2">
    <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl  text-accent text-center mb-16">
      Our story & vision
    </h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[1fr_280px] gap-10 items-start">
      <div class="text-lg leading-relaxed space-y-5">
        <p class="text-justify">
          Aïkku, founded in October 2024 by Philippe Nougaillon and Sébastien Pourchaire — each with over 30 years of experience — alongside Pierre-Emmanuel Dacquet, was born from a field observation: in many organizations, tools no longer keep up with real-world usage.
          <br>
          <br>
          Fragmented processes, scattered solutions, and increasing complexity for teams meant what seemed like a temporary issue became a structural challenge.
          This reality led to the creation of Aïkku, with a central belief:
        </p>
        <blockquote class="border-l-2 border-accent text-justify md:text-left pl-5 italic font-medium">
          Technology must adapt to organizations, not the other way around.
        </blockquote>
        <p class="text-justify">
          Our ambition is to design scalable platforms built to last, helping teams better plan, coordinate, and track activity through co-construction with users.
          <br>
          <br>
          Every solution we build follows a simple goal: simplify existing systems, improve efficiency, and provide a smooth experience for daily users.
          Our motto is FROM CLIENT TO CODE - FROM CODE TO CLIENT!
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="sticky top-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-accent mb-4">
          Proven expertise
        </p>
        <ul class="divide-y divide-gray-100 space-y-0">
          <li class="py-4 first:pt-0">
            <p class="text-xs font-medium text-accent/70 tracking-wider mb-1">Sectors</p>
            <p class="text-sm">Higher education</p>
            <p class="text-sm">Public sector</p>
            <p class="text-sm">Pharmaceutical industry</p>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-accent">
          Awards
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-0">
          <li class="py-4">
            <p class="text-xs font-medium text-accent/70 uppercase tracking-wider mb-1">2010 — SNCF / TGV Lab</p>
            <p class="text-sm font-medium mb-1">2nd place in innovation contest</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">Mobile application for improving onboard information flow on trains.</p>
          </li>
          <li class="py-4 pb-0">
            <p class="text-xs font-medium text-accent/70 uppercase tracking-wider mb-1">2015 — VINCI / ETF</p>
            <p class="text-sm font-medium mb-1">Île-de-France Innovation Award</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">Railway maintenance tracking solution (AEMMS).</p>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="pb-20 px-16 md:px-30">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-10">
      <div class="md:w-2/3">
        <h1 class="text-2xl md:text-2xl font-medium text-accent uppercase tracking-widest text-center">
          A Message from Our Founders        </h1>
        <div class="mt-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-justify">
          <p>
            Face to the sheer power of AI, which we have integrated into our products and work processes,
            we are convinced that our true value lies in the sustainable support we provide to our clients.
          </p>
          <br/>
          <p>
            With more than 30 years of experience, we make a difference at every stage of the project, 
            from the initial definition of requirements to the full adoption of the application across your entire organization.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-12 flex flex-col items-start ">
          <p class="text-2xl text-accent underline decoration-2 decoration-accent/80  font-hurricane ">
            <i>Philnoug & Seb</i>
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-400 mt-1">
            Founders of Aïkku
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="md:w-1/3 flex justify-center gap-4">
        <%= image_tag 'partners/Philippe.jpg',
        class: 'w-40 h-40 md:w-44 md:h-80 rounded-full border-4 border-white object-cover',
        alt: 'Philippe NOUGAILLON' %>
        <%= image_tag 'partners/sebastien.jpg',
        class: 'w-40 h-40 md:w-44 md:h-80 rounded-full border-4 border-white object-cover',
        alt: 'Sébastien POURCHAIRE' %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <div class="footer-wave">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 1200 62" preserveAspectRatio="none">
      <path d="
      M0,62
      Q300,2 600,32
      Q900,62 1200,32
      L1200,62
      L0,62
      Z
    " fill="#1f1f3d"/>
    </svg>
  </div>
  <section id="secteurs" class="w-full text-white px-10 py-20 md:p-20 bg-info">
    <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-5xl text-center mb-12">Our <span class="text-gradient">team</span></h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mt-16">
      <div class="bg-white h-full border border-gray-100 rounded-xl p-7 flex flex-col gap-4">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
          <%= image_tag 'partners/pierreemmanuel.jpg',
          class: 'w-30 h-30 rounded-full object-cover grayscale opacity-70 hover:grayscale-0 hover:opacity-100 transition-all duration-300 shrink-0',
          alt: 'Pierre-Emmanuel DACQUET' %>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-base text-accent leading-tight">Pierre-Emmanuel Dacquet</h4>
            <p class="italic text-sm text-gray-400">Aka P-E</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mt-1">Developer & digital innovation</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-justify leading-relaxed text-gray-600 border-t border-gray-100 pt-4">
          Trained at Tech&Code Factory and WebSchool Factory, P-E represents a new generation of digital talent combining design, development, and innovation. He was mentored by Philippe Nougaillon on real-world projects from early on. He builds user-centered solutions with a strong focus on innovation and business performance.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-auto flex justify-end border-t border-gray-100 pt-3">
          <%= link_to "https://www.linkedin.com/in/pierre-emmanuel-dacquet", class: 'flex items-center gap-1.5 text-xs font-medium text-accent' do %>
            <%= icon("linkedin", class: "w-6 h-6 ") %></i> LinkedIn
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-xl p-7 flex flex-col gap-4">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
        <%= image_tag 'partners/daniela.jpg',
          class: 'w-30 h-30 rounded-full object-cover grayscale opacity-70 hover:grayscale-0 hover:opacity-100 transition-all duration-300 shrink-0',
          alt: 'Daniela ISAZA HURTADO' %>
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-bold text-base text-accent leading-tight">Daniela Isaza Hurtado</h4>
          <p class="italic text-sm text-gray-400">Aka Dani</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mt-1">Developer & UX designer</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-sm text-justify leading-relaxed text-gray-600 border-t border-gray-100 pt-4">
        After several professional experiences, Dani transitioned into IT, where she found her vocation. She completed a one-year training at Ada Tech School before joining Aïkku through Philippe Nougaillon's mentorship. Committed and continuously improving, she places strong emphasis on solution quality and user experience.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-auto flex justify-end border-t border-gray-100 pt-3">
        <%= link_to "https://www.linkedin.com/in/danielais/", class: 'flex items-center gap-1.5 text-xs font-medium text-accent' do %>
          <%= icon("linkedin", class: "w-6 h-6 ") %></i> LinkedIn
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-xl p-7 flex flex-col gap-4">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
      <%= image_tag 'partners/alexandre.jpg',
          class: ' w-30 h-30 rounded-full object-cover grayscale opacity-70 hover:grayscale-0 hover:opacity-100 transition-all duration-300 shrink-0',
          alt: 'Alexandre MEUNIER' %>
      <div>
        <h4 class="font-bold text-base text-accent leading-tight">Alexandre Meunier</h4>
        <p class="italic text-sm text-gray-400">Aka Alex</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mt-1">Backend engineer — CNAM apprentice</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="text-sm text-justify leading-relaxed text-gray-600 border-t border-gray-100 pt-4">
      Alex is pursuing an engineering degree in computer science and information systems at CNAM. Over a 3-year apprenticeship, he specializes in software development, with a strong focus on backend systems, architecture, and optimization. Rigorous and curious, he values deep understanding and efficient system design.
    </p>
    <div class="mt-auto flex justify-end border-t border-gray-100 pt-3">
      <%= link_to "https://www.linkedin.com/in/alexandre-meunier-0366b9287/", class: 'flex items-center gap-1.5 text-xs font-medium text-accent' do %>
        <%= icon("linkedin", class: "w-6 h-6 ") %></i> LinkedIn
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-xl p-7 flex flex-col gap-4">
  <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
    <%= image_tag 'partners/Philippe.jpg',
          class: 'w-30 h-30 rounded-full object-cover grayscale opacity-70 hover:grayscale-0 hover:opacity-100 transition-all duration-300 shrink-0',
          alt: 'Philippe NOUGAILLON' %>
    <div>
      <h4 class="font-bold text-base text-accent leading-tight">Philippe Nougaillon</h4>
      <p class="italic text-sm text-gray-400">Aka Philnoug</p>
      <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mt-1">Entrepreneur, developer & mentor — 30+ years</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <p class="text-sm text-justify leading-relaxed text-gray-600 border-t border-gray-100 pt-4">
    Philnoug is an entrepreneur, developer, consultant, and open-source enthusiast with over 30 years of experience. Expert in XP / RAD / AGILE / LEAN / SCRUM approaches, he has led more than 50 projects and developed several open-source applications. He also works as a mentor and trainer, supporting young developers and product managers.
  </p>
  <div class="mt-auto flex justify-end border-t border-gray-100 pt-3">
    <%= link_to "https://www.linkedin.com/in/philnoug/", class: 'flex items-center gap-1.5 text-xs font-medium text-accent' do %>
      <%= icon("linkedin", class: "w-6 h-6 ") %></i> LinkedIn
  <% end %>
</div>
</div>
<div class="bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-xl p-7 flex flex-col gap-4">
  <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
    <%= image_tag 'partners/serena.jpg',
          class: 'w-30 h-30 rounded-full object-cover grayscale opacity-70 hover:grayscale-0 hover:opacity-100 transition-all duration-300 shrink-0',
          alt: 'Serena PINALI' %>
    <div>
      <h4 class="font-bold text-base text-accent leading-tight">Serena Pinali</h4>
      <p class="italic text-sm text-gray-400">Aka Nuna</p>
      <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mt-1">Product Manager & communications</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <p class="text-sm text-justify leading-relaxed text-gray-600 border-t border-gray-100 pt-4">
    With a certified Product Manager degree (RNCP level 7) and strong experience in community management and training, Nuna manages digital projects at Aïkku as well as marketing, communication, and client/developer relations. She is cheerful, agile, and persistent, always striving for improvement.
  </p>
  <div class="mt-auto flex justify-end border-t border-gray-100 pt-3">
    <%= link_to "https://www.linkedin.com/in/serena-pinali", class: 'flex items-center gap-1.5 text-xs font-medium text-accent' do %>
      <%= icon("linkedin", class: "w-6 h-6 ") %></i> LinkedIn
  <% end %>
</div>
</div>
<div class="bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-xl p-7 flex flex-col gap-4">
  <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
    <%= image_tag 'partners/sebastien.jpg',
          class: 'w-30 h-30 rounded-full object-cover grayscale opacity-70 hover:grayscale-0 hover:opacity-100 transition-all duration-300 shrink-0',
          alt: 'Sébastien POURCHAIRE' %>
    <div>
      <h4 class="font-bold text-base text-accent leading-tight">Sébastien Pourchaire</h4>
      <p class="italic text-sm text-gray-400">Aka Seb</p>
      <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mt-1">Healthcare IS expert — 30+ years</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <p class="text-sm text-justify leading-relaxed text-gray-600 border-t border-gray-100 pt-4">
    Seb has over 30 years of experience in healthcare information systems. He focuses on digital transformation, data standardization, and user support. He strongly believes in training and support as keys to success and builds solutions aimed at optimizing organizational performance.
  </p>
  <div class="mt-auto flex justify-end border-t border-gray-100 pt-3">
    <%= link_to "https://www.linkedin.com/in/pourchaire", class: 'flex items-center gap-1.5 text-xs font-medium text-accent' do %>
      <%= icon("linkedin", class: "w-6 h-6 ") %></i> LinkedIn
  <% end %>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<div class="footer-wave">
  <svg viewBox="0 0 1200 60" preserveAspectRatio="none">
    <path d="
      M0,0
      Q300,60 600,30
      Q900,0 1200,30
      L1200,0
      L0,0
      Z
    " fill="#1f1f3d"/>
  </svg>
</div>
<section id="avis" class="min-h-screen px-6 md:px-20 pb-20 pt-10">
  <h2 class="text-center text-4xl lg:text-5xl  text-accent mb-12">
    Client testimonials
  </h2>
  <div class="flex flex-col justify-center gap-16">
    <div class="bg-white shadow-xl rounded-2xl p-8 flex flex-col border border-gray-100">
      <%= icon("quote", class: "w-6 h-6 mb-4 text-left text-accent ") %></i>
    <p class="text-gray-700 text-justify leading-relaxed text-sm md:text-base">
      I had the opportunity to collaborate with Philippe from the Aïkku team on many projects, including a European project. He demonstrates great professionalism, combining listening skills, understanding, and creativity. He excels at translating needs into agile, robust, and sustainable solutions. Always exploring open-source technologies, he proposes simple, efficient, and well-adapted solutions. Accessible and pedagogical, he provides structured support and innovative approaches. I highly recommend him.
    </p>
    <div class="mt-8 border-t pt-6">
      <%= link_to "https://www.linkedin.com/in/philippe-eynaud-3a3ab835/", 
               class: "flex items-center gap-1.5 font-medium text-accent " do %>
        <%= icon("linkedin", class: "w-6 h-6 ") %> Philippe EYNAUD
      <% end %>
      <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">
        Professor of Management Sciences at IAE Paris, University Paris 1 Panthéon-Sorbonne
        <br>
        Author of
        <%= link_to "'The management of information systems in its complexity'", 
                          "https://www.amazon.fr/management-syst%C3%A8me-dinformation-dans-complexit%C3%A9/dp/1784055026/ref=sr_1_5?qid=1687595735", 
                          class: "link italic no-underline", target: '_blank' %>. (2018) ISTE Editions.  
        <br>
        Author of 
        <%= link_to "'Dictionary of a different management'", 
                      "https://www.editions-eres.com/ouvrage/5545/dictionnaire-dune-autre-gestion", 
                      class: "italic link no-underline", target: '_blank' %>, (2026), érés Editions.  
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="bg-white shadow-xl rounded-2xl p-8 flex flex-col border border-gray-100">
    <%= icon("quote", class: "w-6 h-6 mb-4 text-left text-accent ") %></i>
  <p class="text-gray-700 text-justify leading-relaxed text-sm md:text-base">
    I had the pleasure of working with the Aïkku team on the deployment of the Planning-IAE tool. What a great experience! The Aïkku team embodies the “user orientation” I teach my students. They listen carefully and translate user needs into concrete solutions through co-construction. Philippe is reliable, responsive, and very pleasant to work with. The result is a central tool, quickly adopted and able to evolve with needs. A smooth and effective collaboration that I highly recommend.
  </p>
  <div class="mt-8 border-t pt-6">
    <%= link_to "https://www.linkedin.com/in/marieevelaporte/", 
               class: "flex items-center gap-1.5 font-medium text-accent " do %>
      <%= icon("linkedin", class: "w-6 h-6 ") %> Marie-Eve LAPORTE
    <% end %>
    <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">
      Professor, "Innovation Management & Future of Healthcare" research chair
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 ">
  <div class="bg-white shadow-xl rounded-2xl p-8 flex flex-col border border-gray-100">
    <%= icon("quote", class: "w-6 h-6 mb-4 text-left text-accent ") %></i>
  <p class="text-gray-700 text-justify leading-relaxed text-sm md:text-base">
    The Aïkku team listened carefully and perfectly met our needs.
    I highly recommend them.
  </p>
  <div class="mt-8 border-t pt-6">
    <%= link_to "https://www.linkedin.com/in/christophe-pallandre/", 
               class: "flex items-center gap-1.5 font-medium text-accent " do %>
      <%= icon("linkedin", class: "w-6 h-6 ") %> Christophe PALLANDRE
    <% end %>
    <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">
      CFO Western Europe @ Grohe France
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="bg-white shadow-xl rounded-2xl p-8 flex flex-col border border-gray-100">
  <%= icon("quote", class: "w-6 h-6 mb-4 text-left text-accent ") %></i>
<p class="text-gray-700 text-justify leading-relaxed text-sm md:text-base">
  Philippe is a great teacher and taught me a lot. He helped me gain confidence by taking the time to guide me through problem-solving. Very involved and up to date with the latest technologies, he is a serious and committed professional.
</p>
<div class="mt-8 border-t pt-6">
  <%= link_to "https://www.linkedin.com/in/alexandre-cukier/", 
               class: "flex items-center gap-1.5 font-medium text-accent " do %>
    <%= icon("linkedin", class: "w-6 h-6 ") %> Alexandre CUKIER
  <% end %>
  <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">
    Backend Engineer @ Firefly 
  </p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>